OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Meta CEO Mark Zuckerberg has apologised
OL,6, to families who say their children had 
OL,7, been harmed by social media, during a  
OL,8, fiery hearing in the US Senate.        
OL,10,FMr Zuckerberg - who runs Instagram and 
OL,11,FFacebook - turned to them and said     
OL,12,F"no-one should go through" what they   
OL,13,Fhad.                                   
OL,15,FHe and the bosses of TikTok, Snap, X   
OL,16,Fand Discord were questioned for almost 
OL,17,Ffour hours by senators from both       
OL,18,Fparties.                               
OL,20,FLawmakers wanted to know what they are 
OL,21,Fdoing to protect children online.      
